    <!-- Onboarding permissions page -->
    <string name="onboarding_perm_title">A few permissions, then we\'re set</string>
    <string name="onboarding_perm_subtitle">PawPill works fully offline. These permissions only help us deliver reminders on time — nothing leaves your phone.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_perm_notifications_why">So we can tap you on the shoulder the moment a dose is due. Without this, the app can\'t remind you at all.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_perm_exact_alarms_why">Reminders need to fire at the precise minute you scheduled — not \"sometime in the next hour.\"</string>
    <string name="onboarding_perm_battery_why">Some phones aggressively kill background apps. This stops Android from snoozing your reminders.</string>
